# Privacy Policy

## 1. Privacy at a Glance

### General Information

The following notes provide a simple overview of what happens to your personal
data when you visit this website.  Personal data is any data by which you can be
personally identified.

### Data Collection on This Website

**Who is responsible for data collection on this website?**

Data processing on this website is carried out by the website operator.
You can find their contact details in the legal notice (Impressum) of this website.

